        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer45393363" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7939673260105838454">Weird, weird, weird. Was hoping for quality since it was an international best seller, and who knows, maybe it was just too high-brow for me, but I didn&apos;t enjoy it. It concentrates on how communism makes people lose their humanity and become just desire-less, shallow, and brain dead. There are a lot of really uncomfortable sex scenes involving children and others in which the act is just humorous and emotion-less, not even erotic just mechanical but not for the usual reasons of boredom with a pa</span>
  <span id="freeText7939673260105838454" style="display:none">Weird, weird, weird. Was hoping for quality since it was an international best seller, and who knows, maybe it was just too high-brow for me, but I didn't enjoy it. It concentrates on how communism makes people lose their humanity and become just desire-less, shallow, and brain dead. There are a lot of really uncomfortable sex scenes involving children and others in which the act is just humorous and emotion-less, not even erotic just mechanical but not for the usual reasons of boredom with a partner but just boredom with the act itself. I don't know. He was shooting for a message of people becoming disattached from living because of the politics, but it was just weird. Wouldn't recommend it. </span>
